{"tid":1427311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我被一個反送中既page block左","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T17:19:11.000Z","uid":223537,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"34cf2f44492874bbed5f7845ca4ac0b13faa6fe4","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"[朋友借ac ]<br />\n<br />\n話說有一日我碌碌下fb見到個賣 tee嘅廣告<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRGfLQB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRGfLQB.png&h=43678fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係一個賣反送中tee既page 由於本人都係做呢⾏<br />\n所以就㩒入 去睇下詳情啦 <br />\n結果發現佢賣緊$80蚊⼀一件 (本⼈做左呢行都係好短時間，經 驗尚淺，但根據已有知識，佢賣 $80其實係賺緊好多)<br />\n<br />\n到佢扣除成本後會捐款，⽽佢個 fb都有講第一輪捐左<span style=\"color: red;\">$10004</span>比612 基⾦金，不過我覺得此數字有少少唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQacN4N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQacN4N.png&h=8aa240ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以本⼈僅有嘅知識，cheap cheap 地⼀件衫，<span style=\"color: red;\">成本約$21-$23</span><br />\n好少少就$25-$30 (單色單logo) (可能佢真係用好靚料好貴我唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⾒識少 <br />\n<br />\n假設: 比盡佢$40一件成本，咁即係一件 賺到$40<br />\n$10004/$40=250件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXjdxxr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXjdxxr.png&h=0880651a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但睇佢呢個post，3000幾個留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⼤大部分都係問價，當只有10 份1⼈人真係會買，咁都有<span style=\"color: red;\">300件</span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係，⼜有可能係有⼀部分既 收入係嚟自第一輪捐款之後，可能第二輪會捐好多比立場呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲嘢我都無從得知喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然見佢咁有心，唔想佢比啲好似我咁既⼈人誤會<br />\n加上佢仲有係fb到落廣告，更易比⼈人懷疑架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是就留左個言問下佢 「介唔介意公開成本係幾多?」 公開數目大家都清楚，咁好人就會 ⼀⽣平安啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後加上當⽇睇左好多關於前線學生為左買gear而冇錢開飯既報導 心諗:「有錢買tee不如直接捐左錢先」 <br />\n<br />\n就係留言到加多左句:「當見到前線學生冇錢食飯時，一件咁樣既 tee係咪真係咁重要呢?有錢既話 不如直接捐」 (由於冇諗過會比佢block<br />\n<br />\n所以冇cap低個留言) 對唔住，或者我既言論太偏激啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過左幾日我就發現⾃己比佢地block左喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCkL77p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCkL77p.png&h=18ef0a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLike唔到留唔到言 <br />\n關於佢地賣衫既post都已經睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDeMSzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDeMSzu.png&h=3f763654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗住同佢地了解下咩事，既然大家都係反送中既同路人<br />\n如果我有做錯嘅地方，都想同佢地say個 sorry<br />\n點知連pm個掣都冇左<br />\n其實我都認同要為呢場運動做個記錄，整啲紀念品做icon<br />\n不過見到前線學⽣冇錢開飯，⽽佢地仲咁溫馨著親子裝，我真係於⼼不忍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇⼈人可以話我知點解個page會 block左我?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：朋友不是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8389b1315a162a78ead148bdcc0bc1bec5a80b3b","tid":1427311,"uid":124496,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"食人血饅頭 發死人財"},{"pid":"70233147ab7dc55b3d28e78bf49447ac50837b33","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8389b1315a162a78ead148bdcc0bc1bec5a80b3b","tid":1427311,"uid":124496,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"食人血饅頭 發死人財"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"2b2bee2b82acf96eeb3eacb2cc349466cc2a1ab7","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"17f32ea6981b8e2f85e5c9ffc723f986d842b330","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"光後香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"2fa195ed82272658fc6fea8ced28d3a6550cf94d","tid":1427311,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8389b1315a162a78ead148bdcc0bc1bec5a80b3b","tid":1427311,"uid":124496,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"食人血饅頭 發死人財"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[找亮點]到底係狗扮暴徒定有黑社會扮狗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同浸大學生會會長有關！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry for標題差"},{"pid":"f9f3573874abd28c5b44d00ab5cb6592ed826bfc","tid":1427311,"uid":52504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51c6fed8e7dd572b18aad372f1990534c1bf8075","tid":1427311,"uid":52504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a548ca8d22a68eec01af6fcf9aabd1114d758719","tid":1427311,"uid":33776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"cd68e26805660789fdaa280d0caa15aa4ad6dc34","tid":1427311,"uid":277536,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"間野發國難財<br />\n如果係同路人點會咁就block你，擺明身有屎啦。<br />\n<br />\n祝佢死全家，早日考黑犬成功"},{"pid":"5d402fc9585da2e77d813ffd7da608bd4d78a11d","tid":1427311,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79fefa1afd437255049c4678dc63041cdcda7700","tid":1427311,"uid":120757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e626b8759568c2ef8bedf22c60c6e283501d92b","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">人血饅頭！</span>"},{"pid":"863ac982d9bfb417be2d509bd5f9108647b345e7","tid":1427311,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf77634d49227d13545406e0dc3e200d339bb9bf","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"成個fb comment 好和諧啊 個個都淨係問幾錢咁乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e833bdb541a867781aa5eea1d0444e91b4f18c","tid":1427311,"uid":94510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:52:11.000Z","msg":"推啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec6bfd0ecf6a50f33d02cb64532d258ca4d3dd1","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人幫襯啊喂 第二輪實捐到十幾萬俾立場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78622e4919794eab6d745c2f9ce65947f5e6de13","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a3d7b1912320f47e21bf11df351175ad37e15846","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2eddae2ae696758508b95248c259efdb218a9c0e","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:51:36.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1bb8fadcab975863cd5838f021520b43b1145e76","tid":1427311,"uid":201504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00c54080acd6268ab9b42dde36b031f48c32f8b0","tid":1427311,"uid":272424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:42.000Z","msg":"100內ok la"},{"pid":"9805bbd7ac5ae47fb3eeb21e13e91a5b0d85194b","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c54080acd6268ab9b42dde36b031f48c32f8b0","tid":1427311,"uid":272424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:42.000Z","msg":"100內ok la"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"賺你60蚊之後捐返10蚊 自己賺50蚊<br />\n呢個係講緊最最最保守個價 實際係更多<br />\n再同你講扣除成本 將所有錢捐出嚟 <br />\n吸引人買 覺得自己買咗就可以俾到錢前線<br />\n咁樣嘅人血饅頭你都覺得ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d3abb8a48cf7ae83ad3a1a806f60112af522a2","tid":1427311,"uid":223537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f82be5b0d7ee462b0223881f6623efa4b7547633","tid":1427311,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:22:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}